Attribution
-----------

This project is a fork of
  https://github.com/riccardoperra/better-comments-for-github
by Riccardo Perra, distributed under the Apache License 2.0.

The block-based Markdown editor, prosekit integration, slash commands,
toolbar, table handling, code-block features, GitHub node support,
URL-parsing / page-detection / textarea-handling infrastructure, and the
build pipeline (WXT configuration, monorepo layout, markdown-schema /
markdown-transformer packages) all originate from the upstream project.
Upstream copyright notices in source file headers have been preserved.


Modifications in this fork
--------------------------

Per Apache 2.0 section 4(b), notable changes introduced by the Scribe fork
include:

- Package scope rename: @better-comments-for-github/* -> @scribe/*.
- Extension identity: manifest name "Better comments for GitHub" is now
  "Scribe"; zip artifact renamed; icon artwork replaced with the
  Nib-Block mark.
- New review-comment prefix system:
    - src/core/custom/comment-prefix/               (new directory)
      - comment-prefix-config.ts
      - comment-prefix.ts
      - comment-prefix-decoration.ts
      - comment-prefix.test.ts
    - src/core/editor/missing-prefix-warning/       (new directory)
      - missing-prefix-warning.tsx
      - missing-prefix-warning.module.css
    - src/core/editor/settings/prefix-settings.tsx  (new file)
    - src/core/editor/settings/prefix-settings.module.css (new file)
- New rendered-comment tinter content script:
    - extension/src/utils/renderedCommentTinter.ts  (new file)
- Modifications to wire the prefix feature through the editor:
    - src/core/editor/extension.ts                   (extended)
    - src/core/editor/slash-menu/slash-menu.tsx      (extended)
    - src/core/editor/toolbar/toolbar.tsx            (extended)
    - src/core/editor/settings/settings.tsx          (extended)
    - src/core/editor/editor.tsx                     (extended)
    - src/actions.ts                                 (extended)
    - src/editor/editor.tsx                          (extended)
    - src/render.tsx                                 (extended)
    - extension/src/entrypoints/editor-content.ts   (extended)
- Removal of the upstream landing site (landing/ directory).
- Replacement of logo and brand marketing assets.
- Documentation rewrite (README.md).
- pnpm-workspace adjustments to drop the landing workspace.

Files modified by this fork retain their original upstream Apache 2.0
headers unchanged. Files newly created for this fork carry Apache 2.0
headers identifying the Scribe fork copyright.
